CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 17, 2005

[Cite as 05/17/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-2377.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2004-2050. Camelot Distrib. Co., Inc. v. Stark Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2003-M-24. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
